                        <h2>The Closest Comparison in Cold Email</h2>
                        <p>Saleshandy and Instantly are the most directly comparable cold email tools on the market. Both offer unlimited email accounts, built-in warm-up, automated sequences, and flat-rate pricing starting around $36–37/month. The differences are meaningful but not dramatic — this is a genuine toss-up for many buyers.</p>
                        <p>Instantly wins on deliverability infrastructure, UI quality, and community size. Its warm-up network is larger, its interface is cleaner, and it has a significantly larger community of power users sharing templates, best practices, and campaign strategies. For most individual SDRs and small teams, Instantly is the better default choice.</p>
                        <p>Saleshandy wins on entry-level unlimited accounts (available from $36/month vs Instantly's $97/month Growth plan) and on the built-in B2B lead database. For agencies managing multiple client domains who want unlimited accounts at the absolute lowest cost, Saleshandy is the better choice at the entry tier.</p>
                    </section>

