                    <section class="content-section" id="where-it-breaks">
                        <h2>Where Each Tool Breaks</h2>
                        <p><strong>Saleshandy breaks</strong> when you need the best UI or the largest community. Its interface is functional but less polished than Instantly, and the smaller community means fewer public resources for troubleshooting and optimization. The built-in lead database is useful but not enterprise-grade.</p>
                        <p><strong>Instantly breaks</strong> when you need unlimited accounts at the lowest possible price. Its unlimited accounts feature requires the Growth plan ($97/month) — the entry Sending Warmup plan ($37/month) limits connected accounts. For agencies managing 20+ domains on a tight budget, Saleshandy's entry-tier unlimited accounts is a meaningful advantage.</p>
